description: The Planet Earth is a remarkable place.  Home to millions of species of life, the only known place in the Universe where it could exist, Earth is also humanity's home.  With this free ebook you can learn everything you would ever want to know about this wonderous planet.  This book provides a detailed overview of major topics about the Earth including its history, composition, geology, tectonics, atmosphere, position in the solar system, its moon and even the different cultures that it hosts.  Download this title today and learn about your planet on the go!
